id: pm-bl8x
title: "ADR: workspace scale-out strategy — indexed reads, storage fan-out, and bounded-output contracts for 100k-1M-item workspaces (proposed)"
description: "Proposed ADR (open=proposed, close=accepted per pm-m2u1 convention) that fixes the ground rules for the scale-out initiative epic. Duplicate check 2026-07-06: searched scalability/sharding/index/pagination — no existing open or closed item covers workspace-scale architecture."
