risk: high
confidence: medium
resolution: "Accepted: versioned rebuildable derived index, hash-bucket migration contract, stable opaque cursors with scale-threshold bounded defaults, per-item lock scaling, and advisory Git/history growth policy"
expected_result: "Scale implementation has an SDK-first, Git-native architecture contract with explicit correctness and fallback rules"
actual_result: Decision grounded in local 10k/100k benchmark evidence and linked to canonical implementation items; hosted GitHub performance workloads excluded
